projects.name: Real Time Language Translator
projects.description: Whenever we go to different place there will be language barrier to overcome that barrier we have to know the language speak in that place or we should have language translator. The second is easier than the first one so I decided to create a language translator. I have done a project named Real Time Language Translator which helps in translating one language to another which having around two hundred languages available. I have achieved this one using HTML,CSS,JavaScript,Express,Node Js,Mongodb.
